		<credit project="CfPBoK@https://slebok.github.io/cfpbok/"/>
		<h1>Tag <code>T4C</code>: Vertical Transformation</h1>
		Generative + Compilation + Refinement + Recovery. Work about shifting abstraction levels downwards: compilation, code generation, model-to-text transformations, refinement, synthesis, lowering, as well as extraction, recovery, reverse engineering techniques that raise abstraction. If the key novelty is the transformation language itself rather than the pipeline or the implementation, we consider <a href="t3b.html">T3B</a>.
